<div class="highlight">
📢 Apply Online: 15 April 2026 to 15 May 2026
</div>

<h2>📄 Article (Full Details)</h2>

<p>
Bihar Technical Service Commission (BTSC) has released the official notification for 
<strong>Instructor Recruitment 2026</strong>. A total of <b>726 posts</b> are available for various trades. 
Candidates who have completed <b>ITI in relevant trade</b> can apply for this recruitment.
</p>

<p>
The online application process will start from <b>15 April 2026</b> and the last date to apply is 
<b>15 May 2026</b>. Interested candidates are advised to read the full notification carefully before applying.
</p>

<p>
This is a great opportunity for ITI pass candidates to get a government job in Bihar. 
Selection will be done as per BTSC rules.
</p>

